04"><div begin="00:00.314" end="03:10.404"><p begin="00:00.314" end="00:04.130" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:00.314" end="00:00.579">I've</span> <span begin="00:00.579" end="00:00.776">been</span> <span begin="00:00.776" end="00:01.075">dream</span><span begin="00:01.075" end="00:01.240">in'</span> <span begin="00:01.240" end="00:01.513">'bout</span> <span begin="00:01.513" end="00:01.743">the</span> <span begin="00:01.743" end="00:02.150">West</span> <span begin="00:02.150" end="00:03.729">Coast</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:02.677" end="00:04.130"><span begin="00:02.677" end="00:03.120">(I've</span> <span begin="00:03.120" end="00:03.358">been</span> <span begin="00:03.358" end="00:03.799">dream</span><span begin="00:03.799" end="00:04.130">in')</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直在梦想</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直梦想着西海岸</span></p><p begin="00:04.050" end="00:08.692" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:04.050" end="00:04.297">Found</span> <span begin="00:04.297" end="00:04.528">some</span> <span begin="00:04.528" end="00:04.990">faces</span> <span begin="00:04.990" end="00:05.219">that</span> <span begin="00:05.219" end="00:05.443">I</span> <span begin="00:05.443" end="00:05.952">don't</span> <span begin="00:05.952" end="00:07.980">know</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:06.344" end="00:08.692"><span begin="00:06.344" end="00:06.821">(I've</span> <span begin="00:06.821" end="00:07.022">been</span> <span begin="00:07.022" end="00:07.516">dream</span><span begin="00:07.516" end="00:07.750">in'</span> <span begin="00:07.750" end="00:08.322">about</span> <span begin="00:08.322" end="00:08.692">it)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直在做这样的梦</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">邂逅一些陌生的面孔</span></p><p begin="00:08.435" end="00:11.649" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:08.435" end="00:08.685">Give</span> <span begin="00:08.685" end="00:08.911">me</span> <span begin="00:08.911" end="00:08.980">the</span> <span begin="00:08.980" end="00:09.759">sun</span> <span begin="00:09.759" end="00:10.001">for</span> <span begin="00:10.001" end="00:10.530">just</span> <span begin="00:10.530" end="00:10.630">a</span> <span begin="00:10.630" end="00:11.649">year</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让阳光温暖我 一年就好</span></p><p begin="00:12.116" end="00:15.453" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:12.116" end="00:12.324">I'll</span> <span begin="00:12.324" end="00:12.559">kiss</span> <span begin="00:12.559" end="00:12.650">the</span> <span begin="00:12.650" end="00:13.519">sky</span> <span begin="00:13.519" end="00:13.767">and</span> <span begin="00:13.767" end="00:14.259">dis</span><span begin="00:14.259" end="00:15.453">appear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会亲吻天空 然后消失不见</span></p><p begin="00:16.484" end="00:19.569" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:16.484" end="00:16.736">I've</span> <span begin="00:16.736" end="00:16.867">been</span> <span begin="00:16.867" end="00:17.187">star</span><span begin="00:17.187" end="00:17.422">in'</span> <span begin="00:17.422" end="00:17.847">up</span> <span begin="00:17.847" end="00:18.052">at</span> <span begin="00:18.052" end="00:18.267">the</span> <span begin="00:18.267" end="00:18.803">greyest</span> <span begin="00:18.803" end="00:19.569">skies</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直仰头凝视着昏暗的天空</span></p><p begin="00:19.595" end="00:23.067" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:19.595" end="00:19.835">Try</span><span begin="00:19.835" end="00:19.959">na</span> <span begin="00:19.959" end="00:20.324">find</span> <span begin="00:20.324" end="00:20.395">my</span><span begin="00:20.395" end="00:20.683">self</span> <span begin="00:20.683" end="00:20.945">some</span> <span begin="00:20.945" end="00:21.353">luck,</span> <span begin="00:21.441" end="00:21.617">but</span> <span begin="00:21.617" end="00:21.927">it's</span> <span begin="00:21.927" end="00:22.113">run</span><span begin="00:22.113" end="00:22.553">nin'</span> <span begin="00:22.553" end="00:23.067">dry</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着找到我自己的幸运 但是希望愈发渺茫</span></p><p begin="00:23.091" end="00:26.837" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:23.091" end="00:23.241">It's</span> <span begin="00:23.241" end="00:23.457">like</span> <span begin="00:23.457" end="00:23.682">the</span> <span begin="00:23.682" end="00:24.135">weather</span> <span begin="00:24.135" end="00:24.351">makes</span> <span begin="00:24.351" end="00:24.587">the</span> <span begin="00:24.587" end="00:25.024">worst</span> <span begin="00:25.024" end="00:25.197">of</span> <span begin="00:25.197" end="00:25.461">my</span> <span begin="00:25.461" end="00:26.156">cloudy</span> <span begin="00:26.156" end="00:26.837">mind</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就好像糟糕的天气让我的内心也布满阴云</span></p><p begin="00:26.858" end="00:30.522" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:26.858" end="00:26.998">I</span> <span begin="00:26.998" end="00:27.110">could</span> <span begin="00:27.110" end="00:27.715">really</span> <span begin="00:27.715" end="00:27.869">use</span> <span begin="00:27.869" end="00:28.136">a</span> <span begin="00:28.136" end="00:28.600">dose</span> <span begin="00:28.600" end="00:28.699">of</span> <span begin="00:28.699" end="00:29.032">some</span> <span begin="00:29.032" end="00:29.511">par</span><span begin="00:29.511" end="00:30.522">adise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我真想让天堂来治愈一下我</span></p><p begin="00:30.548" end="00:33.748" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:30.548" end="00:30.820">Some</span><span begin="00:30.820" end="00:31.067">times</span> <span begin="00:31.067" end="00:31.265">you</span> <span begin="00:31.265" end="00:31.509">got</span><span begin="00:31.509" end="00:31.744">ta</span> <span begin="00:31.744" end="00:32.094">run</span> <span begin="00:32.094" end="00:32.411">from</span> <span begin="00:32.411" end="00:32.595">a</span> <span begin="00:32.595" end="00:32.863">bro</span><span begin="00:32.863" end="00:33.280">ken</span> <span begin="00:33.280" end="00:33.748">heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有时候你必须逃离破碎的心</span></p><p begin="00:33.771" end="00:37.308" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:33.771" end="00:33.903">Be</span><span begin="00:33.903" end="00:34.204">fore</span> <span begin="00:34.204" end="00:34.377">I</span> <span begin="00:34.377" end="00:34.669">turn</span> <span begin="00:34.669" end="00:35.095">into</span> <span begin="00:35.095" end="00:35.307">a</span> <span begin="00:35.307" end="00:35.767">ghost,</span> <span begin="00:35.767" end="00:36.020">need</span> <span begin="00:36.020" end="00:36.188">a</span> <span begin="00:36.188" end="00:36.445">brand-</span><span begin="00:36.445" end="00:36.670">new</span> <span begin="00:36.670" end="00:37.308">start</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在我变成孤魂野鬼之前 我需要全新的开始</span></p><p begin="00:37.339" end="00:40.915" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:37.339" end="00:37.568">Get</span> <span begin="00:37.568" end="00:37.693">my</span><span begin="00:37.693" end="00:37.948">self</span> <span begin="00:37.948" end="00:38.249">head</span><span begin="00:38.249" end="00:38.454">ed</span> <span begin="00:38.454" end="00:38.687">to</span> <span begin="00:38.687" end="00:38.865">the</span> <span begin="00:38.865" end="00:39.367">coast,</span> <span begin="00:39.367" end="00:39.594">man,</span> <span begin="00:39.594" end="00:39.818">it</span> <span begin="00:39.818" end="00:40.020">ain't</span> <span begin="00:40.020" end="00:40.352">that</span> <span begin="00:40.352" end="00:40.915">far</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让我向着海岸进发 伙计 那里并没有太远</span></p><p begin="00:40.924" end="00:44.714" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:40.924" end="00:41.142">Yeah,</span> <span begin="00:41.142" end="00:41.356">they</span> <span begin="00:41.356" end="00:41.498">got</span> <span begin="00:41.498" end="00:41.833">sun</span> <span begin="00:41.833" end="00:42.040">in</span> <span begin="00:42.040" end="00:42.239">L</span><span begin="00:42.239" end="00:42.610">A</span> <span begin="00:42.915" end="00:43.093">and</span> <span begin="00:43.093" end="00:43.265">some</span> <span begin="00:43.265" end="00:43.723">shin</span><span begin="00:43.723" end="00:43.898">in'</span> <span begin="00:43.898" end="00:44.714">stars</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是的 洛杉矶有太阳 还有闪耀的星星</span></p><p begin="00:44.714" end="00:48.281" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:44.714" end="00:44.956">I've</span> <span begin="00:44.956" end="00:45.141">been</span> <span begin="00:45.141" end="00:45.430">dream</span><span begin="00:45.430" end="00:45.609">in'</span> <span begin="00:45.609" end="00:45.832">'bout</span> <span begin="00:45.832" end="00:46.072">the</span> <span begin="00:46.072" end="00:46.462">West</span> <span begin="00:46.462" end="00:48.128">Coast</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:46.970" end="00:48.281"><span begin="00:46.970" end="00:47.408">(I've</span> <span begin="00:47.408" end="00:47.641">been</span> <span begin="00:47.641" end="00:48.050">dream</span><span begin="00:48.050" end="00:48.281">in')</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直在梦想</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直梦想着西海岸</span></p><p begin="00:48.294" end="00:52.599" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:48.294" end="00:48.513">Found</span> <span begin="00:48.513" end="00:48.734">some</span> <span begin="00:48.734" end="00:49.221">faces</span> <span begin="00:49.221" end="00:49.417">that</span> <span begin="00:49.417" end="00:49.665">I</span> <span begin="00:49.665" end="00:50.099">don't</span> <span begin="00:50.099" end="00:52.066">know</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:50.550" end="00:52.599"><span begin="00:50.550" end="00:50.993">(I've</span> <span begin="00:50.993" end="00:51.218">been</span> <span begin="00:51.218" end="00:51.663">dream</span><span begin="00:51.663" end="00:51.888">in'</span> <span begin="00:51.888" end="00:52.360">about</span> <span begin="00:52.360" end="00:52.599">it)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直在做这样的梦</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">邂逅一些陌生的面孔</span></p><p begin="00:52.614" end="00:55.729" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:52.614" end="00:53.138">Seein'</span> <span begin="00:53.138" end="00:53.820">signs</span> <span begin="00:53.820" end="00:54.086">for</span> <span begin="00:54.086" end="00:54.712">Cali</span><span begin="00:54.712" end="00:55.242">for</span><span begin="00:55.242" end="00:55.729">nia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">看见加州的标志出现在眼前</span></p><p begin="00:56.340" end="00:59.019" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:56.340" end="00:56.591">Trade</span> <span begin="00:56.591" end="00:56.696">the</span> <span begin="00:56.696" end="00:57.465">shade</span> <span begin="00:57.465" end="00:57.576">for</span> <span begin="00:57.576" end="00:58.088">some</span><span begin="00:58.088" end="00:58.384">thin'</span> <span begin="00:58.384" end="00:59.019">warmer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将内心的阴霾用温暖的阳光替代</span></p><p begin="00:59.043" end="01:02.586" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:59.043" end="00:59.293">I've</span> <span begin="00:59.293" end="00:59.493">been</span> <span begin="00:59.493" end="00:59.748">dream</span><span begin="00:59.748" end="00:59.966">in'</span> <span begin="00:59.966" end="01:00.187">'bout</span> <span begin="01:00.187" end="01:00.398">the</span> <span begin="01:00.398" end="01:00.789">West</span> <span begin="01:00.789" end="01:02.459">Coast</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:01.294" end="01:02.586"><span begin="01:01.294" end="01:01.742">(I've</span> <span begin="01:01.742" end="01:01.974">been</span> <span begin="01:01.974" end="01:02.371">dream</span><span begin="01:02.371" end="01:02.586">in')</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直在梦想</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直梦想着西海岸</span></p><p begin="01:02.608" end="01:07.107" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:02.608" end="01:02.868">Where</span> <span begin="01:02.868" end="01:03.081">the</span> <span begin="01:03.081" end="01:03.494">people</span> <span begin="01:03.494" end="01:03.734">take</span> <span begin="01:03.734" end="01:03.976">it</span> <span begin="01:03.976" end="01:04.231">real</span> <span begin="01:04.231" end="01:06.702">slow</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:04.897" end="01:07.107"><span begin="01:04.897" end="01:05.319">(I've</span> <span begin="01:05.319" end="01:05.550">been</span> <span begin="01:05.550" end="01:05.992">dream</span><span begin="01:05.992" end="01:06.215">in'</span> <span begin="01:06.215" end="01:06.891">about</span> <span begin="01:06.891" end="01:07.107">it)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那是我梦寐以求的地方</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那里的生活节奏真的很慢</span></p><p begin="01:06.879" end="01:09.862" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:06.879" end="01:07.119">I</span> <span begin="01:07.119" end="01:07.338">need</span> <span begin="01:07.338" end="01:07.434">the</span> <span begin="01:07.434" end="01:08.159">sun</span> <span begin="01:08.159" end="01:08.393">for</span> <span begin="01:08.393" end="01:08.951">just</span> <span begin="01:08.951" end="01:09.098">a</span> <span begin="01:09.098" end="01:09.862">year</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我需要阳光 一年就好</span></p><p begin="01:10.460" end="01:14.051" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:10.460" end="01:10.671">I'll</span> <span begin="01:10.671" end="01:10.901">kiss</span> <span begin="01:10.901" end="01:10.979">the</span> <span begin="01:10.979" end="01:11.802">sky</span> <span begin="01:11.802" end="01:12.044">and</span> <span begin="01:12.044" end="01:12.533">dis</span><span begin="01:12.533" end="01:14.051">appear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我会亲吻天空 然后消失不见</span></p><p begin="01:14.069" end="01:17.162" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:14.069" end="01:14.242">Ain't</span> <span begin="01:14.242" end="01:14.580">felt</span> <span begin="01:14.580" end="01:14.729">a</span> <span begin="01:14.729" end="01:15.168">drop</span> <span begin="01:15.168" end="01:15.388">now</span> <span begin="01:15.388" end="01:15.549">for</span> <span begin="01:15.549" end="01:16.298">forty</span> <span begin="01:16.298" end="01:17.162">days</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经四十天没有下过雨</span></p><p begin="01:17.162" end="01:20.695" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:17.162" end="01:17.232">But</span> <span begin="01:17.232" end="01:17.626">still,</span> <span begin="01:17.626" end="01:17.869">they're</span> <span begin="01:17.869" end="01:18.087">wash</span><span begin="01:18.087" end="01:18.312">ing</span> <span begin="01:18.312" end="01:18.743">cars,</span> <span begin="01:18.743" end="01:18.852">and</span> <span begin="01:18.852" end="01:18.994">they</span> <span begin="01:18.994" end="01:19.152">don't</span> <span begin="01:19.152" end="01:19.447">show</span> <span begin="01:19.447" end="01:19.885">any</span> <span begin="01:19.885" end="01:20.695">age</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但是他们仍在洗车 它们没有显露出任何岁月的痕迹</span></p><p begin="01:20.736" end="01:24.026" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:20.736" end="01:20.999">Ain't</span> <span begin="01:20.999" end="01:21.200">noth</span><span begin="01:21.200" end="01:21.433">in'</span> <span begin="01:21.433" end="01:21.621">that</span> <span begin="01:21.621" end="01:21.895">you</span> <span begin="01:21.895" end="01:2